description: "Set up PostCSS with autoprefixer and optimization plugins.\n\n**File to create:** `/Users/fadymondy/Sites/orchestra-app/packages/design-system/adapters/web/postcss.config.js`\n\n**Code:**\n```javascript\nexport default {\n  plugins: {\n    tailwindcss: {},\n    autoprefixer: {},\n  },\n};\n```\n\n**File to create:** `/Users/fadymondy/Sites/orchestra-app/packages/design-system/adapters/web/README.md`\n\n**Content:**\n```markdown\n# Orchestra Web Adapter\n\nWeb/Electron adapter for the Orchestra Design System with Tailwind CSS 4.\n\n## Installation\n\n\\`\\`\\`bash\npnpm add @orchestra/adapter-web @orchestra/tokens @orchestra/components\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n## Usage\n\n### 1. Import the base styles\n\nIn your main entry file:\n\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nimport '@orchestra/adapter-web/styles';\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### 2. Configure Tailwind\n\nIn your \\`tailwind.config.ts\\`:\n\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nimport orchestraConfig from '@orchestra/adapter-web/tailwind';\n\nexport default {\n  ...orchestraConfig,\n  content: [\n    './src/**/*.{ts,tsx}',\n    // Add your content paths\n  ],\n};\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### 3. Initialize the theme engine\n\n\\`\\`\\`typescript\nimport { initThemeEngine } from '@orchestra/tokens';\n\ninitThemeEngine('orchestra');\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n### 4. Wrap your app with ThemeProvider\n\n\\`\\`\\`tsx\nimport { ThemeProvider } from '@orchestra/components';\n\nfunction App() {\n  return (\n    <ThemeProvider defaultTheme=\"orchestra\">\n      {/* Your app */}\n    </ThemeProvider>\n  );\n}\n\\`\\`\\`\n\n## Features\n\n- Tailwind CSS 4 integration\n- Design system CSS variables\n- Optimized build output\n- Theme-aware utilities\n- PostCSS processing\n\\`\\`\\`"
